---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const steps = [
  {
    n: "01", title: "Collect", tag: "30+ sources",
    desc: "Over 30 active data sources scrape Telegram, RSS, blockchains, exchanges, government filings, and social media around the clock.",
  },
  {
    n: "02", title: "Classify", tag: "llm classify pool",
    desc: "An LLM pool tags every event into one of 13 signal types — with direction, confidence, and asset scope. A local model anchors the pool, with extra lanes absorbing burst volume so classification keeps pace with the feed.",
  },
  {
    n: "03", title: "Corroborate", tag: "cross-referenced",
    desc: "The signal processor cross-references multiple sources. A whale alert backed by a funding rate spike and a news headline scores higher than any single source alone.",
  },
  {
    n: "04", title: "Anchor", tag: "macro pulse · 07:00 utc",
    desc: "Macro Pulse runs daily. It ingests the upcoming USD high-impact calendar — FOMC, CPI, NFP, PPI — plus 7 days of intel signals, and emits a directional bias for BTC and ETH. Trades that contradict a high-conviction macro call are downgraded or vetoed.",
  },
  {
    n: "05", title: "Deliver", tag: "rest · ws · webhook · mcp",
    desc: "Signals hit your system via REST API, WebSocket, or Webhook — within seconds of detection. Free tier gets a 15-minute delay. Pro gets real-time + Macro Pulse access.",
  },
];
---

<BaseLayout
  title="about"
  description="n0brains is a crypto signal API. 30+ watchers monitor Telegram, blockchains, exchanges, filings, and social around the clock; an LLM pipeline classifies, corroborates, and scores every event. You get the signal. You decide what to do with it."
>
  <section class="about-page">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="ab-hero">
      <div class="ab-hero-grid" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <p class="ab-kicker"><span class="ab-dash"></span><span data-scramble>about · the audit desk</span></p>
      <h1 class="ab-h1">RAW DATA IN.<br /><span class="accent">SIGNALS OUT.</span></h1>
      <p class="ab-lede">
        <strong>n0brains</strong> is a crypto signal API. Over 30 watchers
        monitor Telegram, blockchains, exchanges, government filings, and social
        media around the clock. An LLM classification pool tags every event,
        cross-references across sources, and scores it for confidence — before
        the opportunity disappears.
      </p>
      <p class="ab-signoff">You get the signal. You decide what to do with it.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 01 · how it works -->
    <div class="ab-section">
      <div class="ab-side">
        <div class="ab-label">01 · how it works</div>
        <div class="ab-side-title">FIVE STEPS,<br />EVERY SECOND.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-body">
        <div class="ab-steps">
          {steps.map((s, i) => (
            <div class="ab-step">
              <div class="ab-step-rail">
                <div class="ab-step-num">{s.n}</div>
                {i < steps.length - 1 && <div class="ab-step-line"><span></span></div>}
              </div>
              <div class="ab-step-text">
                <div class="ab-step-head">
                  <span class="ab-step-title">{s.title}</span>
                  <span class="ab-step-tag">{s.tag}</span>
                </div>
                <p>{s.desc}</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 02 · why this exists -->
    <div class="ab-section">
      <div class="ab-side">
        <div class="ab-label">02 · why this exists</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-body ab-prose">
        <p>The best crypto signals aren't locked behind $500/month paywalls or exclusive Discord groups. They're hiding in plain sight: on-chain flows, whale wallets, funding rates, government filings, a dozen free data sources.</p>
        <blockquote class="ab-quote">The edge isn't the data — it's connecting it fast enough to act.</blockquote>
        <p>Most people can't watch a dozen feeds at once. Most people can't cross-reference a whale alert against a funding rate spike and a Senate committee vote in the 90 seconds before the market moves. A machine can — and then it scores the result, so you act on one number, not twelve tabs.</p>
        <p><strong>Free-tier first.</strong> The pipeline is built on free and public data wherever possible — Alchemy, Etherscan, mempool.space, RSS, Telegram, exchange WebSockets, government filings. If a source goes down or starts charging, we replace it. The product is the synthesis, not the data.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 03 · for agents -->
    <div class="ab-section">
      <div class="ab-side">
        <div class="ab-label">03 · for agents</div>
      </div>
      <div class="ab-body">
        <div class="ab-terminal">
          <div class="ab-term-head"><span class="ab-term-dot"></span>built for autonomous agents first. humans second.</div>
          <div class="ab-term-body">
            <p>The API is the product. There is no dashboard. There is no app.</p>
            <p>If you run an OpenClaw agent, a custom bot, or any system that needs crypto intelligence piped in programmatically — this is for you. Point your agent at the endpoint, give it your API key, and let it trade. Or skip the HTTP client entirely:</p>
            {/* Kept byte-identical to /docs/cli — verify there before changing. */}
            <pre class="ab-cli"><span class="p">$</span> pip install n0brains-cli
<span class="p">$</span> export N0BRAINS_API_KEY=intel_sk_...
<span class="p">$</span> n0brains signals --proven-only --limit 10</pre>
            <div class="ab-term-row"><span>free</span><span class="white">60 req/min · 15-min delay · evaluate the data first</span></div>
            <div class="ab-term-row"><span>pro</span><span class="white">600 req/min · real-time · $39.99/mo · no tiers above it</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="ab-final">// Think Less, Ship More<br />// brain not required</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <style>
    .about-page { max-width: 1100px; margin: 0 auto; }

    /* ── Hero ── */
    .ab-hero { position: relative; padding: 2rem 0 4rem; }
    .ab-hero-grid {
      position: absolute; inset: -40px -10% 0; pointer-events: none;
      background-image:
        linear-gradient(var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px),
        linear-gradient(90deg, var(--border) 1px, transparent 1px);
      background-size: 54px 54px;
      -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 70% at 30% 25%, #000 0%, transparent 75%);
      mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 50% 70% at 30% 25%, #000 0%, transparent 75%);
      opacity: 0.5;
    }
    .ab-kicker {
      position: relative;
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.69rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.25em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 18px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px;
    }
    .ab-dash { display: block; width: 32px; height: 1px; background: var(--accent); }
    .ab-h1 {
      position: relative; margin: 0;
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(3.4rem, 9vw, 6.5rem);
      font-weight: 400; line-height: 0.9; letter-spacing: 0.02em;
      color: var(--text-heading);
    }
    .ab-h1 .accent { color: var(--accent); text-shadow: 0 0 40px var(--accent-glow-strong); }
    .ab-lede {
      position: relative;
      font-size: 1.03rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text);
      max-width: 560px; margin: 28px 0 0;
    }
    .ab-lede strong { color: var(--text-heading); font-weight: 500; }
    .ab-signoff {
      position: relative;
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.82rem;
      color: var(--text-heading); margin: 20px 0 0;
    }

    /* ── Section scaffold ── */
    .ab-section {
      position: relative;
      display: grid; grid-template-columns: 300px 1fr; gap: 48px;
      padding: 64px 0 72px;
    }
    .ab-section::before {
      content: ""; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; right: 0; height: 1px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--border-accent) 25%, var(--border) 50%, var(--border) 75%, transparent);
    }
    @media (max-width: 860px) {
      .ab-section { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 20px; padding: 44px 0 48px; }
    }
    .ab-label {
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.69rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.3em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-faint);
      margin-bottom: 14px;
    }
    .ab-side-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display); font-size: 2.5rem; line-height: 0.95;
      letter-spacing: 0.03em; color: var(--text-heading);
    }
    .ab-body { max-width: 640px; }

    /* ── Steps flow ── */
    .ab-steps { display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
    .ab-step { display: flex; gap: 22px; }
    .ab-step-rail { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; width: 44px; flex-shrink: 0; }
    .ab-step-num {
      width: 38px; height: 38px; border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,65,0.3);
      border-radius: 50%; background: var(--bg-card);
      display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--accent); flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    .ab-step-line {
      width: 2px; flex: 1; background: var(--border);
      overflow: hidden; position: relative; margin: 6px 0;
    }
    .ab-step-line span {
      position: absolute; inset: -20px 0 0;
      background: repeating-linear-gradient(0deg, transparent 0 12px, var(--accent) 12px 20px);
      animation: abFlowV 1.3s linear infinite;
      opacity: 0.7;
    }
    @keyframes abFlowV { from { transform: translateY(-20px); } to { transform: translateY(0); } }
    .ab-step-text { padding-bottom: 30px; }
    .ab-step-head { display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 6px; }
    .ab-step-title { font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 600; color: var(--text-heading); }
    .ab-step-tag {
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.63rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.12em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-faint);
    }
    .ab-step-text p { margin: 0; font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text); }

    /* ── Prose ── */
    .ab-prose p { font-size: 0.97rem; line-height: 1.8; margin: 0 0 18px; color: var(--text); }
    .ab-prose p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
    .ab-prose strong { color: var(--text-heading); font-weight: 500; }
    .ab-quote {
      border-left: 2px solid var(--accent);
      background: rgba(0,255,65,0.025);
      padding: 14px 22px; margin: 0 0 18px;
      color: var(--text-heading); font-style: italic;
      font-size: 1rem; line-height: 1.7;
    }

    /* ── Agents terminal card ── */
    .ab-terminal {
      background: var(--bg-code); border: 1px solid rgba(0,255,65,0.2);
      border-radius: var(--radius); overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 0 44px -20px var(--accent-glow-strong);
    }
    .ab-term-head {
      display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 12px 18px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.63rem;
      letter-spacing: 0.22em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent);
    }
    .ab-term-dot {
      width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%; background: var(--accent);
      animation: abPulse 2s infinite; flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    @keyframes abPulse { 0%,100% { opacity: 1; } 50% { opacity: 0.3; } }
    .ab-term-body { padding: 22px 24px; }
    .ab-term-body p { margin: 0 0 14px; font-size: 0.94rem; line-height: 1.75; color: var(--text); }
    .ab-cli {
      background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: var(--radius-sm); padding: 14px 18px; margin: 0 0 18px;
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.75rem; line-height: 2;
      color: #ccc; overflow-x: auto;
    }
    .ab-cli .p { color: var(--accent); }
    .ab-term-row {
      display: flex; justify-content: space-between; gap: 10px;
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.69rem; color: var(--text-muted);
      padding: 10px 0 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .ab-term-row .white { color: var(--text-heading); text-align: right; }
    .ab-final {
      margin: 36px 0 0;
      font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 0.82rem; line-height: 1.9;
      color: var(--text-muted);
    }
  </style>
</BaseLayout>
